title: IT Parliamentary Committee questions Home Ministry over whether internet shutdowns work
description: Home Ministry did not confirm to the Parliamentary Committee if it had ordered the internet shutdown in Delhi during the anti-CAA protests.

title: Ahead of Market: 12 things that will decide stock action on Wednesday
description: Vinod Nair of Geojit Financial Services said, volatility is expected going forward, but the market will maintain its optimism in-line with stock-wise Q2 result, size of the domestic stimulus and global developments.
